{"tid":1127899,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾勸棄保赴台李倩怡回港 林榮基今認錯：呢2年睇唔到法庭公正","createTime":"2019-04-27T12:19:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T12:26:07.000Z","uid":150685,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a045d813edd710edd76eef8b84df5c6dffba10ba","tid":1127899,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T12:19:28.000Z","msg":"前銅鑼灣書店店長林榮基流亡台灣的消息流出後，有網民「翻炒」他過去訪問提及，會勸因旺角騷亂而被控暴動及襲警罪、棄保潛逃台灣的少女李倩怡回港。他昨日接受《蘋果》訪問時坦然認錯，稱自己只是一個普通人，對香港問題亦有看錯之時，以為李的控罪不會成立，才想勸她回港，「當然我要負責，我係睇錯咗，我相信法庭係公正，但呢兩年睇唔到，2個後生被控暴動判6、7年」。他說，唯一安慰是李來台後未受傷害，「依家睇返轉頭，佢係唔適宜返香港」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190427/59535995\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190427%2F59535995&d=wHiIeFeeqtLxwJ75m5qcs1iy1AgKJyIubMvfhItfpFI%3D&h=6996992f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190427%2F59535995&h=26c2a310\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190427/59535995</a>"},{"pid":"58626cdbf6f033ab387d9e63cc3a9f054e84ae27","tid":1127899,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T12:20:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f64f23fd1163dedfa3534f76cf8f8b0f078e6f9","tid":1127899,"uid":182933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T12:24:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0fb1f34a5f823e14be5d8caca939b97527bdf691","tid":1127899,"uid":3860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T12:26:07.000Z","msg":"泛民其他大佬都出黎切腹認錯啦"}]}